prodNameC: “詩干地巴底”促腎上腺皮質刺激素放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1.ACTH Standards：One set of standards consists of seven vials containing lyophilized serum with synthetic ACTH peptide.
2.ACTH Controls：One set of controls consists of two vials containing ACTH in lyophilized serum with 0.1% (w/v) sodium azide.
3.ACTH 125I-Antibody：One set of tracer consists of two bottles of 125I-anti ACTH (24-39). Each bottle contains polyclonal goat anti ACTH (24-39) antibody which is labeled with 125I and dissolved in 5 ml phosphate buffered saline with sodium azide 0.1% (w/v) and protein stabilizers. The maximum radioactivity in a bottle is <370 kBq (<10μCi).
4.ACTH Antibody Coated Tubes：2 packages of 100 polystyrene tubes (12 x 75 mm diameter) plus desiccant. The tubes are coated with goat anti-ACTH (1-16) antibody. The desiccant contains silica.
5.Wash Concentrate：One bottle contains 30 ml of 30 fold concentrate of phosphate buffered saline with sodium azide 1.5% (w/v) and detergent.
